Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! God damn it! {marsd note: original in braces and we use BrE}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The neccesary conditions for an ESP-card experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would a Level Zero Kamijou-san know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine Breaker, the mysterious ability residing in my right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that any unnatural power will be cancelled just being in contact with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this 'oh-so-wonderful' ability holds no benefits{has no benefit} towards the summer vacation homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}August the 31st
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:01:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make matters worse, Misaka Mikoto forced me to pretend to be her boyfriend on that day... {Even worse on a day like this, I got forced to pretend to be a boyfriend by Misaka Mikoto,}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while some Aztec magician chased after me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and many horrible incidents happened subsequently ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The result? I've{The result was that I have} effectively finished none of my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in Magical Powered Kanamin,{<- name of show}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they use plastic to replicate 'Lotus Wand' and 'Parts of Ether in Elemental.'{<- dont ask me}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese way of doing things sure is magnificent. {ty}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, Index-san, {do we want honorifics in this series?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you to stop watching TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but please keep the volume low at leas-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma won't play with me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm immersing myself in{escaping into} the world of television!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Why are you always giving me more stuff to do when I'm so short on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey where did my half-finished worksheet go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did my classic literature workbook go? And my math reference book?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already past three o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like some snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Index Librorvm Prohibitorvm... {HOLY SHIT it actually exists www.odan.org/index_forbidden_books.doc}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Index of Forbidden Books, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,550)\bord2\3a&H00&\pos(700,370)\fnKozuka Mincho Pro H\b1\c&HE4E0E2&}August 31st
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, what an arduous task of finding the worksheet under a mountain of comic books.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Touma, aren't I worthy of praise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have something you need to say to me?{You should have something you need to say to me, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to imply{ say}? {get to - juz cuz >implying brb pee}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did a lot of work, so I want proper compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I want something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just had{ate} pudding, including mine{y portion}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That looks nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hirayama Rami's 5h Cooking\N"How to make soy bean rich Toufu Hamburger"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we will be demonstrating{teaching} hamburgers{hamburgs} that take five hours to make!{we will be demonstrating how to make hamburgers in 5 hours!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've said{Like I said,} I have no time to make that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently it's past five in the evening and just about seven hours before the day is over.{change of the day. change of day is fucking weird phrase but w/e}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I pull an all-nighter, I have less than fifteen hours before I have to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just this little{much} time left...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bad for your health to{wrong to} work under so much stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mind might slip to a{ become an even} worse state if you're so stressed.{ get so worked up.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overwork yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last person I want to hear that from!{to tell me that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {So here's }the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow of Wind Spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow of Striking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a bad feeling about something{I sense something bad happening}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I order anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most expensive thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want 2,000 yen worth of raw eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Index and I, Kamijou Touma went to a family restaurant for a change of environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed I started my battle against the remaining forces of summer vacation homework...{O_O?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waitin-ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now enter the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My report for Introduction to Ability Development...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh... I'll bring something to wipe it off right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Touma, it's still legible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already wrote three pages...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have to copy it onto a new sheet of paper.{essay paper}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky that you don't have to think up of the content afresh{from the beginning}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now declare the start {shall announce the beginning }of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow of Destructive Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not foresee this outcome{expect this result}, but I will be glad with{shall be happy there is going to be} only a few{less} needless casualties.{inb4 NEEDLESS... oops}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not harm you if{If} you surrender now.{, I won't do any harm to you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I attain what I came here for-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My homework got turned into{became} confetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take responsibility for what you did!{You did this, so take responsibility!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Redo my homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou-san is somewhat violent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will finish the job quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not wish to participate in child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should already understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that this is the Index of Forbidden books with 103,000 books in its memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.{filled by timer}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow of Transparent Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just grabbed hold of something small and soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there, Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, dear customer... {we are here to sell you lots of cheap gold.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I didn't give her have a phone for such situations...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, she wouldn't pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Where should I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going Sphinx?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be in there?{Don't tell me she's kept in there.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there{Is she that way}, Sphinx?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have the least bit of gratitude towards your owner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the circumstances, it was Index who found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already removed two knots in this short period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culture of using ropes in torture originated in Japan.{Using ropes is an original torture culture invented in Japan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to force anything out of me by using such a crude method.{But with such a crude method, you can't make me speak. **}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've said before that my goal is not to torture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only wish to acquire a volume from the collection of magic books within you.{From the magic books within you, I just want to have one volume from the collection.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll first have to create an amplifying magic boundary.{First I need to make a magic boundary for amplification.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\an8}If you bought this you were ripped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is that magician planning to do with Index?{What is that magician going to do to Index?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I be searching?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always seem to be running about somewhere.{It looks like you're always running around.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me know if you're doing all right!{tell me you're doing all right if you are so!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, you don't have{didn't know} my number...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit acting stupid-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look like you're just about to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry, like a real hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homework, kidnapping and some incident at the restaurant and other stuff!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, what's your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... Just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just annoyed that you ignored me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing serious or anything but... nothing serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're really leaving me here like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this supposed to be a Kagura stage?{need explanation for Kagura? orz spiritual music and dancing as an offering to the gods}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8\fs25}Note: Kagura - Spiritual music and dancing as an offering to the gods
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is nothing that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would only pass to be the dance stage of a summer festival at best.{It's rather a summer festival dance stage at best.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to have something possess me by preparing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My purpose for creating this magic boundary is to increase this thing's ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Azusa bow?{azusa = catalpa}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ceremonial object used in Shinto practise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even cover the cultural traditions of the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against that magic book library of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey Index, where are you now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this ability will only be able to jolt your mind and correct distortions at best with its original scale of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However under the right conditions{all set right}, it can read the opponents mind in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:13:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I can even reveal those 103,000 books you secretly hold in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No you mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, you know what will happen when someone other than myself comes in contact with the magic books!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be more sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hotel from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Baopuzi - Master who Embraces Simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic book of eternal life from the Sinosphere on becoming an immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Written in it is Chinese alchemy with instructions for the reader to make medicine to cure any disease or curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would be able to do anything if I became a Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I vowed to become a Magician because I didn't want to give up against a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least not for this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a woman nearly dead from some sort of curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With death approaching right behind her, the only thing she could do was smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a powerless, boring person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being unable to save such a boring person,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot talk{there is no talking} about being able to do anything or not wanting to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot ruin the precious dream I've always had for such a boring woman.{For such a boring woman I cannot ruin the(can't hurt my) precious dream I've always had.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely{It's surely} not for that boring woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely not{It's never} for the sake of that boring woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.{see what's wrong.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Azusa bow's power is amplified so much that your mind is flowing back into mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply because you love that woman{You only loved that woman.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is why you want to save her even at the cost of{even if it cost you} your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had to hurt others and commit crimes in your bid to save her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you didn't want that woman to bear any responsibility.{throw that reponsibilty to that woman.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why you must not taint yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot choose such a method that relies on these half-tainted magic books!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez you made me worry.{you caused so much worrying.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll let you have all the water you can drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I mistaken to feel the need to protect someone even if it cost me my life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain of having someone precious die in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having someone being hurt and in agony right before you...{in front of you be hurt and feel agony...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you being unable to do anything for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the pain of being powerless...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have felt time was running out, the weight of the burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have felt distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have felt anguish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have felt fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have shouted out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what you're doing is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot let anyone carry such a burden!{shock!/suffering?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in this state after just reading one volume... {Just reading one volume left me in this state.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:18:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it was impossible to take in even one original copy in such a small vessel like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life consists only of failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have already given up on life three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one thing I couldn't give up... just that one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have such a peaceful death{nice boat ending}. {I won't let you finish off neatly like that alone.}{NO YOU NOOO WHERES MY NICEBOAT NICE BOATO NAISU BOOOAAATTTOOO check your anus it's there}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for ruining my summer homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you it's impossible for me to finish my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that important person of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:18:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you don't need to use the Index of Forbidden Books to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen what my right hand can do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am no magician, so I don't know what curses are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with this, I can probably erase some curse with a touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it well myself, but that's how my right hand works.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will surely save that important person of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to do that I'll need your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will have you help me no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to save her with your own power too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic and curses and all that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting thrown around the place with that weird stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's set off to break all those stupid illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,250)}Text on fan: "Imouto"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who you've just attacked...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Knights that England is so proud of are in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.77,0:22:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've not been told to stop you as an individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have my work too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the order come from, the Anglican Church or the Academy City?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well it should be easy to figure out if you use some common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, you would figure it out easily if you take into account which side I'm spying for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to report to your superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I'll put them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, why did you need to take this long journey from England?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\3a&H00&\fnKozuka Mincho Pro H\b1\fs70\c&HCCAF71&\pos(419,144)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Index has been kidnapped suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge plot is taking place outside of the Academy City...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the true purpose of the syndicate targeting Orsola Aquinas?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.77,0:23:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Liber AL vel Legis.{the book of the law}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Science and Magic cross, the story begins.
